name: V1.0.0 RC2
body: This would be the final release version if no new commit in March.

name: Version 1.0 (alpha5)
body:
- merge lua 5.3 offical bugfix 
- improve sproto rpc api
- fix a deadlock bug when service retire
- improve cluster config reload
- add skynet.pcall for calling a function with `require`
- better error log in loginserver

name: Version 1.0.0 (alpha 4)
body:
- sproto can share c struct between states
- udp api changed and fix memory leak in dns module

name: Version 1.0 (alpha 3)
body:
- Update sproto (bugfix)
- Add async dns query
- Improve httpc

name: Version 1.0 (alpha 2)
body:
- Update examples client to lua 5.3
- Patch lua 5.3 to interrupt the dead loop (for debug)
- Update sproto (fix some bugs and support unordered map)

name: Version 1.0 (alpha)
body:
This is the first alpha version of skynet 1.0 .
Feedback is welcome , and we will release the beta version in 2 months .

name: Version 0.9.1
body: Forgot merge udp branch last version ;)

name: Version 0.7.4
body:
fix the bug introduce by 0.7.3

Don't use these tag, unless you use this patch : https://github.com/cloudwu/skynet/commit/1ef5430e0ad0ec45ce1d7e9d9b40bf3eb25c21eb
some bugfix , and add httpc module.

name: v0.4.2 : a bugfix version, and some minor features added.
body:
Major changes:
- Add TCP_NODELAY support
- Add worker thread weight
- Add skynet.queue
- skynet.localname return nil when query failed
- Add datacenter.wait
- Add cluster.reload
Major change : New harbor / master module in lua .

name: The third version
body:
## Major feature
- Add cluster support
- Add single node mode
- Add daemon mode

name: Bugfix version for v0.1.0
body:
Bugfix:
1. socket channel reconnect should clear request queue.
2. socket close may block the coroutine.
3. jemalloc api may crash on macosx (disable jemalloc on macosx).
